### Get all users (no filters)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/users

### Get all users with pagination
GET http://localhost:4000/api/users?page=1&limit=10

### Search users by name
GET http://localhost:4000/api/users?search=john

### Filter users by role
GET http://localhost:4000/api/users?role=contractor

### Filter users by location
GET http://localhost:4000/api/users?location=507f1f77bcf86cd799439011

### Filter users by category
GET http://localhost:4000/api/users?category=507f1f77bcf86cd799439012

### Combined filters with pagination
GET http://localhost:4000/api/users?search=john&role=contractor&page=1&limit=5

### Sort users by name ascending
GET http://localhost:4000/api/users?sortBy=full_name&sortOrder=asc

### Sort users by creation date descending (default)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/users?sortBy=createdAt&sortOrder=desc

### Full example with all parameters
GET http://localhost:4000/api/users?search=john&role=contractor&location=507f1f77bcf86cd799439011&category=507f1f77bcf86cd799439012&page=2&limit=20&sortBy=createdAt&sortOrder=desc

###############################################
# Admin User Management Endpoints
###############################################

### Admin: Get all users with pagination
GET http://localhost:4000/api/admin/users?page=1&limit=10

### Admin: Search and filter users
GET http://localhost:4000/api/admin/users?search=john&role=customer&page=1&limit=5

### Admin: Get single user by ID
GET http://localhost:4000/api/admin/users/507f1f77bcf86cd799439011

### Admin: Suspend user
PATCH http://localhost:4000/api/admin/users/507f1f77bcf86cd799439011/suspend
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "suspend": true,
  "reason": "Violation of terms of service"
}

### Admin: Unsuspend user
PATCH http://localhost:4000/api/admin/users/507f1f77bcf86cd799439011/suspend
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "suspend": false
}

### Admin: Delete user
DELETE http://localhost:4000/api/admin/users/507f1f77bcf86cd799439011
